what I'm saying?

29:48.162 --> 29:50.123
See, he does understand.

29:53.084 --> 29:54.127
That's about it.

29:54.294 --> 29:56.421
All we can do now is wait.

30:08.182 --> 30:10.893
I've got to think of my family.

30:12.353 --> 30:14.022
I have children to raise.

30:14.188 --> 30:15.565
So, what if I die?

30:18.651 --> 30:20.987
I am a real estate
agent in the suburbs.

30:21.154 --> 30:24.282
My brother is a
famous movie director.

30:24.449 --> 30:25.575
You're crazy.

30:25.742 --> 30:27.827
You don't know what
you're talking about.

30:27.994 --> 30:31.497
