we don't do the transplant.

30:31.664 --> 30:32.707
I don't care.

30:33.791 --> 30:35.835
He doesn't talk to me.

30:36.002 --> 30:37.754
To this day, he blames
for father's death.

30:37.920 --> 30:41.799
Now that he needs me, he
remembers that I exist.

30:43.593 --> 30:45.636
I already told you, I
want a million dollars,

30:45.803 --> 30:48.014
or I'm going home tomorrow.

30:48.181 --> 30:52.226
I want a check of a
million in my wife's hands,

30:52.393 --> 30:53.686
or I'm not doing the transplant.

30:53.853 --> 30:55.733
But you know we don't
have that sort of money.

30:55.772 --> 30:56.606
You know that.

30:56.773 --> 30:58.483
What do you mean?

30:58.649 --> 31:01.652
How much that house
you live in worth?

31:55.957 --> 31:58.251
Who the fuck are you?

31:58.418 --> 31:59.627
Out.

31:59.794 --> 32:00.794
Out, out!

32:33.911 --> 32:35.329
Are you crazy?

32:36.873 --> 32:41.002
I can't understand where all
this hatred is coming from.

32:41.169 --> 32:44.380
We grew up together,
we shared everything.

32:44.547 --> 32:47.467
We're blood brothers
for God's sake.

32:48.759 --> 32:51.512
All that he has, he worked for.

32:51.679 --> 32:53.556
He never stole anything.

32:55.766 --> 32:57.435
We've reduced
the morphine dosage,

32:57.602 --> 32:59.187
which was very high.

32:59.353 --> 33:01.814
He'll feel pain again, but
there's nothing we can do.

33:01.981 --> 33:04.317
At high levels, the
morphine can cause

33:04.484 --> 33:05.776
a lack of oxygen in his blood

33:05.943 --> 33:09.947
and this may lead to a
cardio respiratory arrest.

34:39.662 --> 34:41.080
I got the money.

34:42.248 --> 34:45.585
Tomorrow, it'll be
in your wife's hands.

34:46.919 --> 34:50.798
