to save his life?

35:15.615 --> 35:16.991
Mind if I smoke?

35:21.954 --> 35:24.040
First time in the States?

35:27.835 --> 35:28.836
No.

35:31.172 --> 35:32.882
Been here many times.

35:34.216 --> 35:37.928
How'd you find
out you were sick?

35:38.095 --> 35:40.806
I was having dinner
with some friends,

35:40.973 --> 35:42.933
one of their wives was a doctor.

35:43.100 --> 35:45.770
