on my neck and she said,

35:45.936 --> 35:47.313
"I don't like this.

35:49.982 --> 35:51.359
When they finished
the procedure,

35:51.525 --> 35:54.654
it was much bigger
than they expected.

35:55.863 --> 35:58.908
