38:41.195 --> 38:43.113
Oh, that's Sissy.

38:43.280 --> 38:44.824
My little girl.

38:44.990 --> 38:48.035
She's been with me
since she was born.

38:48.202 --> 38:50.120
She looks very
much like her mother.

38:51.330 --> 38:54.083
Everyone tells me that.

38:54.250 --> 38:55.334
Same eyes.

39:07.721 --> 39:09.139
August the 6th.

39:09.306 --> 39:10.641
Remember the date well.

39:10.808 --> 39:14.728
From now on, it's going
to be your new birthday.

39:16.522 --> 39:18.566
And now, what do I do?

39:20.234 --> 39:21.986
There's nothing you can do.

39:22.152 --> 39:23.779
Now it's up to him.

39:41.213 --> 39:43.090
This woman, who is she?

39:44.341 --> 39:45.634
I don't know.

39:47.803 --> 39:52.808
It's a woman who follows me
around the whole goddamn time.

39:53.475 --> 39:54.475
She's stuck on me.

39:56.270 --> 39:58.689
