her "I don't love you."

40:02.318 --> 40:05.404
Since we're gonna
be together forever,

40:05.571 --> 40:07.615
could you tell me
where we're heading

40:07.781 --> 40:09.384
- after we leave here?
- Hold on, wait a second.

40:09.408 --> 40:10.826
Who said forever?

40:12.286 --> 40:15.664
Is there something else that
you don't want to tell me?

40:15.831 --> 40:17.374
I just don't know.

40:18.584 --> 40:21.629
They never told me,
and I never asked.

40:23.505 --> 40:27.718
Look, I'm only doing this
because it's steady work, right?

40:27.885 --> 40:30.262
I get my paycheck,
vacation, and, this year,

40:30.429 --> 40:34.099
a bonus trip to
Disneyland for good work.

40:34.266 --> 40:36.060
What does "good work" mean?

40:37.061 --> 40:38.395
Cannot say.

40:38.562 --> 40:39.772
Not authorized.

40:40.940 --> 40:45.027
My contract has a
confidentiality clause.

40:45.194 --> 40:46.362
I just do my job.

40:46.528 --> 40:50.574
I show up, no questions,
don't talk to anyone.

40:50.741 --> 40:51.867
When my boss arrives,

40:52.034 --> 40:53.744
I hide so I don't have
to say good morning.

40:53.911 --> 40:55.829
I'm afraid he'll fire me.

40:57.331 --> 41:01.168
I spend hours staring at
the wall outside my window.

41:01.335 --> 41:04.254
When they remember me, they
ask me to go and fetch someone.

41:04.421 --> 41:07.132
You know, it's a job
I'd rather not do.

41:07.299 --> 41:09.969
Why do you do it, then?

41:10.135 --> 41:13.055
You have a family to support?

41:13.222 --> 41:16.266
