no house, no one.

41:20.938 --> 41:25.734
I have a son, but we had a
fight and we don't talk anymore.

41:27.778 --> 41:29.780
I think he's a skydiver.

41:33.200 --> 41:36.996
I just have this
extremely jealous woman

41:37.162 --> 41:39.206
who always wants
to know what I do,

41:39.373 --> 41:40.833
who I talk to, where I go.

41:41.000 --> 41:43.002
You know how women are, right?

41:43.168 --> 41:44.168
I guess so.

41:45.295 --> 41:46.005
I'm a happy man.

41:46.171 --> 41:47.589
What about you?

41:47.756 --> 41:48.756
Me?

41:49.883 --> 41:51.218
Only on Mondays.

41:52.928 --> 41:54.805
What do you do?

41:54.972 --> 41:57.433
I'm a film director.

41:57.599 --> 41:58.599
Wow.

42:00.185 --> 42:01.185
Wow.

42:01.812 --> 42:02.812
Super.

42:04.523 --> 42:05.899
Are you famous?

42:06.692 --> 42:08.027
I used to be.

42:10.070 --> 42:13.741
In my town, there was a
cinema, but I never went.

42:13.907 --> 42:16.410
Now, it's an evangelical church.

42:17.369 --> 42:19.163
Do you play chess?

42:25.294 --> 42:27.713
Doctor, he's back.

42:29.089 --> 42:30.966
Say something, my love.

42:35.721 --> 42:37.181
What's happening?

42:37.347 --> 42:40.559
Does he have a fever,
is he cold, what is it?

42:40.726 --> 42:43.270
Would you get
some warm blankets, please?

42:43.437 --> 42:44.646
What's going on?

42:44.813 --> 42:46.053
We have to stop this infection

42:46.106 --> 42:47.399
as quickly as possible.

42:47.566 --> 42:50.652
So, we'll be starting on a
broad-spectrum antibiotic,

42:50.819 --> 42:53.697
and take him to intensive
care immediately.

43:23.352 --> 43:25.062
His blood pressure's falling.

43:25.229 --> 43:27.940
The oxygen level is very low,
and his heartbeat is weak.

43:28.107 --> 43:30.192
We're unable to
contain the infection,

43:30.359 --> 43:31.735
and we may lose the patient.

44:01.473 --> 44:05.811
I'm Dr. Feffer and I'm
Jewish, as I believe you are.

44:07.980 --> 44:11.400
My whole family died
in the Warsaw ghetto,

44:13.235 --> 44:16.572
and I was brought up in
an orphanage in London,

44:16.738 --> 44:19.241
where I graduated in medicine.

44:20.409 --> 44:22.452
I emigrated to
the United States,

44:22.619 --> 44:26.373
and I'm one of the
founders of this institute.

44:26.540 --> 44:29.501
We've won a Nobel Prize for
our research into blood.

44:29.668 --> 44:32.671
So, here, we believe
only in science.

44:34.423 --> 44:38.760
