I'd never been to the cinema.

46:16.066 --> 46:18.360
I saw a film of yours.

46:18.527 --> 46:20.529
Do you remember which one?

46:20.696 --> 46:23.448
Well, I don't remember the name,

46:23.615 --> 46:27.536
