a deserted breach,

57:19.228 --> 57:23.441
and she was looking behind her
like someone was chasing her.

57:23.608 --> 57:25.652
She wore a tight sweater,

57:27.153 --> 57:31.866
a black belt, and a full skirt
which billowed in the wind.

57:33.993 --> 57:36.496
There was a group
of boys in a car.

57:36.663 --> 57:39.707
They were drinking,
laughing, shouting.

57:39.874 --> 57:43.044
She was running
away, scared of them.

57:43.211 --> 57:45.797
Their car got closer and closer,

57:45.964 --> 57:48.174
and then she fell, exhausted.

57:50.343 --> 57:52.095
The car circled around her,

57:52.261 --> 57:55.181
the boys were
laughing and shouting.

57:55.348 --> 57:58.101
And then the car stopped.

57:58.267 --> 58:00.770
And one of the boys went to her.

58:02.271 --> 58:04.899
She started crying, desperately.

58:06.484 --> 58:08.277
Sitting in the sand.

58:13.783 --> 58:16.035
And what happened to her?

58:19.789 --> 58:21.165
You know, I don't remember,

58:21.332 --> 58:25.086
but I do remember that
when she got home,

