a flycatcher bird.

1:39:48.275 --> 1:39:52.779
So, one day, the ambulance took
her and she never came back.

1:39:54.031 --> 1:39:56.742
I was by myself at
home for two days.

1:39:56.909 --> 1:39:59.453
No one came to tell me anything.

1:40:00.662 --> 1:40:02.664
